 --------------------------- EDITOR'S NOTE ----------------------------

 http://desktopvideo.about.com
 ------------------------- IN THE SPOTLIGHT ---------------------------
 Capturing Video To Your Computer
 So you bought that camcorder for Christmas - now what do you do? Get a Firewire card and hook it up.
 http://glclk.about.com/?zi=5/79W
 Adobe Tutorial - Chromakey Effect
 How to superimpose something from within Adobe Premiere. This technique is similar for other video editing software packages as well.
 http://glclk.about.com/?zi=5/79X
